        Ilkley, West Yorkshire<br />
        United Kingdom
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm mt-2">
        <a href="mailto:hello@reignites.co.uk" class="hover:text-accent">hello@reignites.co.uk</a><br />
        <a href="tel:+447397897186" class="hover:text-accent">0735 20 50 404</a>
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm mt-3">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com" class="hover:text-accent" rel="noreferrer">Connect on LinkedIn</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
